From the hilarious and twisted minds of Penny Arcade creators Mike "Gabe"
Krahulik and Jerry "Tycho" Holkins, legendary game designer Ron Gilbert and
veteran producers at Hothead Games comes a 100% authentic and hilarious Penny
Arcade experience.

